                  {
                    "cta": "Cool!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to give technical updates at work.\nThis is very useful during team meetings and standups.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/136ef69f-2c49-45b7-9aef-9ace7c9599b5-Technical-update---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "To talk about what you are doing, say:\n\"I'm working on [task]. It's [status].\"\nFor example: \"I'm working on the login page. It's almost done.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/136ef69f-2c49-45b7-9aef-9ace7c9599b5-Technical-update---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "To talk about a system problem, say:\n\"The [system] is [state] right now.\"\nFor example: \"The staging server is down right now.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/136ef69f-2c49-45b7-9aef-9ace7c9599b5-Technical-update---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "To share progress with numbers, say:\n\"[Item] is at [value]. We're [on track / a bit behind].\"\nFor example: \"Test coverage is at 72%. We're a bit behind.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/136ef69f-2c49-45b7-9aef-9ace7c9599b5-Technical-update---1.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Now let's practice giving technical updates!",
                    "media": {
